on_actions = {
	on_unit_leader_created = {
		effect = {
			set_variable = { indexed_id = global.army_leader_ids^num }
			add_to_array = { global.army_leader_ids = THIS.id }
		}
	}
	on_daily = {
		effect = {
			every_state = {
				limit = {
					check_variable = { provinces_on_gas_attack^num > 0 }
				}
			}
		}
	}
	on_monthly = {
		effect = {
			every_state = {
				limit = {
					check_variable = { provinces_on_gas_attack^num > 0 }
				}
				gas_state_event_effect = yes #After capitulation of the controller, some provinces remain gassed forever. This is a bandaid not a fix. I'm really tired at this point and there is only a week before the midterm exams :(
			}
		}
	}
	on_startup = {
		effect = {
			FRA = {
				country_event = { id = ffufrance.3 days = 779 }
				country_event = { id = ffufrance.4 days = 2497 }
			}
			SER = {
				country_event = { id = ww1_franzferdinand.2 days = 1304 }
				country_event = { id = ww1_firstbalkan.4 days = 609 }
				country_event = { id = ww1_firstbalkan.2 days = 578 }
			}
			SWI = {
				country_event = { id = ww1_firstbalkan.40 days = 851 }
			}

			TUR = {
				country_event = { id = ffuottoman.8 days = 1383 }
			}

			every_country={
            			country_event = { id = ffu.2 days = 0 }
			}

			every_country={
				limit={
					is_playable_country=yes
				}
				add_ideas = peace_training
				set_variable = { super_events_enabled = 2 }
			}
			every_country={
				limit={
					is_playable_country=no
				}
				add_ideas = ai_limiter
			}
			every_country = {
				every_army_leader = {
					set_variable = { indexed_id = global.army_leader_ids^num }
					add_to_array = { global.army_leader_ids = THIS.id }
				}
			}
			if = {
				limit = {
					has_game_rule = {
						rule = FFU_navy_race
						option = RACE
					}
				}
				every_country = {
					limit={
						is_playable_country=yes
					}
					transfer_navy = {
						target = SWI
					}
					add_ideas = naval_race
				}
				80 = {
					add_extra_state_shared_building_slots = 7
					add_building_construction = {
						type = dockyard
						level = 7
						instant_build = yes
					}

				}
				5 = {
					add_extra_state_shared_building_slots = 2
					add_building_construction = {
						type = dockyard
						level = 2
						instant_build = yes
					}
				}
			}

			if = {
				limit = { BEL = { is_ai = yes } }
				FRA = {
			         	add_equipment_to_stockpile= {
                        			type = infantry_equipment_1
                        			amount = 50000
                        			producer = FRA
					}
            			}
				55 = {

	on_monthly = {
		effect = {
			SWI = { country_event = { id = ffu.1 } }
			every_country={
				limit = {
					is_playable_country=yes
					NOT = {
						OR = {
							has_war = yes
							has_idea = peace_training
						}
					}
				}
				add_ideas = peace_training
			}
			every_country={
				limit = {
					is_playable_country=yes
					has_game_rule = {
						rule = FFU_navy_race
						option = RACE
					}
					NOT = {
						OR = {
							has_war = yes
							has_idea = naval_race
						}
					}
				}
				add_ideas = naval_race
			}
		}
	}
	on_state_control_changed = {
		effect = {
			if = {
				limit = {
					tag = TUR
					FROM.FROM = { state = 152 }
					FROM = { original_tag = SER }
					NOT = { has_global_flag = balkan_war_over }
				}
				set_global_flag = balkan_war_over
				TUR = {
					country_event = { id = ww1_firstbalkan.200 }
					TUR = { white_peace = SER }
					SER = { white_peace = TUR }
					BUL = { white_peace = TUR }
					GRE = { white_peace = TUR }
					MNT = { white_peace = TUR }
				}
			}
			if = {
				limit = {
					tag = BUL
					NOT = { has_global_flag = ffu_ww1_starts }
					FROM.FROM = { state = 152 }
					FROM = {  OR = { tag = SER tag = GRE tag = ROM } }
					NOT = { has_global_flag = second_balkan_war_over }
				}
				set_global_flag = second_balkan_war_over
				BUL = {
					transfer_state = 134
					transfer_state = 155
					transfer_state = 153
					white_peace = SER
					white_peace = GRE
					white_peace = MNT
					if = {
						limit = {
							BUL = {
								has_war_with = ROM
							}
						}
						white_peace = ROM
					}
				}
			}
			if = {
				limit = {
					OR = {
						tag = SER
						tag = GRE
						tag = ROM
					}
					FROM.FROM = { state = 147 }
					FROM = { original_tag = BUL }
					NOT = { has_global_flag = second_balkan_war_over }
					NOT = { has_global_flag = ffu_ww1_starts }
				}
				set_global_flag = second_balkan_war_over
				GRE = {
					white_peace = BUL
					transfer_state = 133
				}
				SER = {
					white_peace = BUL
					transfer_state = 154
				}
				TUR = {
					white_peace = BUL
					transfer_state = 160
				}
				if = {
					limit = {
						has_global_flag = kis_secondbalkanwar_romanian_intervention
					}
					ROM = {
						white_peace = BUL
						transfer_state = 110
					}
				}
			}
			if = {
					limit = {
						FROM = { tag = BEL }
						FROM.FROM = { is_core_of = BEL }
						BEL = { surrender_progress	> 0.60 }
						NOT = { BEL = { has_country_flag = belgium_is_kill }}}

	         		BEL = {
						set_country_flag = belgium_is_kill
						add_state_core = 35
						set_capital = 35
						transfer_state = 35
						add_ideas = we_fight_on
					  }
					}
	        	}
	        }

	on_capitulation = {
		effect = {
			if = {
				limit = {
					original_tag = BEL
					GER = { has_war_with = BEL }
				}
				teleport_armies = {
					to_state = 55
				}
			}
			if = {
				limit = {
					original_tag = RUS
					SOV = { has_war_with = RUS }
				}
				SOV = {
					annex_country = {
						target = RUS
						transfer_troops = no
					}
				}
			}
			if = {
				limit = {
					original_tag = FIN
					SOV = { has_war_with = FIN }
				}
				SOV = {
					annex_country = {
						target = FIN
						transfer_troops = no
					}
					every_state = {
						limit = {
							# SOV will get the same core as RUS
							#is_claimed_by = RUS
							is_core_of = FIN
						}
						SOV = {
							add_state_core = PREV
						}
					}
				}
			}
		}
	}
}
